{"word":"Azariah","slug":"azariah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Azariah</b> <a href=\"#/H5838\">H5838</a><br/><a href=\"#/H5839\">H5839</a> <br/> 1. Son of Ethan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=8'>1Ch 2:8</a><br/> 2. Son of Jehu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=39'>1Ch 2:39</a><br/> 3. Son of Zadok, perhaps identical with Amariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=2'>1Ki 4:2</a><br/> 4. Captain of Solomon's guards<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=5'>1Ki 4:5</a><br/> 5. A prophet, called Obed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=1'>2Ch 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=8'>2Ch 15:8</a><br/> 6. A high priest, called Amariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=19&verse=11'>2Ch 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=9'>1Ch 6:9</a><br/> 7. Son of Jehoshaphat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=2'>2Ch 21:2</a><br/> 8. King of Judah, called Ahaziah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=6'>2Ch 22:6</a><br/><a href='S:Ahaziah'>Ahaziah</a> <br/> 9. Son of Jeroham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=1'>2Ch 23:1</a><br/> 10. Son of Obed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=1'>2Ch 23:1</a><br/> 11. Son of Johanan, possibly identical with Zechariah, son of Jehoiada<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=11'>1Ch 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=22'>2Ch 24:22</a><br/> 12. See <a href='S:Uzziah'>Uzziah</a>, 1<br/> Uzziah, 1<br/> 13. Chief of the tribe of Ephraim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=12'>2Ch 28:12</a><br/> 14. A Levite, called Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=36'>1Ch 6:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=24'>1Ch 6:24</a><br/> 15. High priest in Hezekiah's reign<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=10'>2Ch 31:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=13'>2Ch 31:13</a> <br/> - Probably identical with Ahitub<br/> 16. Son of Hilkiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=14'>1Ch 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=11'>1Ch 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=1'>Ezr 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=3'>Ezr 7:3</a><br/> 17. Son of Hoshaiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=43&verse=7'>Jer 43:7</a><br/> 18. Hebrew name of Abed-Nego<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=7'>Dan 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1&verse=19'>Dan 1:19</a><br/> 19. A captive returned from Babylon, called Seraiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=7'>Neh 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=2'>Neh 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=2'>Ezr 2:2</a>"}]}